Instructions:

Step 1:

	Select a file by pressing the "Select Files to Convert button"

Step 2:

	Confirm the layout of your PDF in the Preview PDF section (At the top of the application).

Step 3:

	If you like the layout, skip to Step 5. If you would like to change/fix anything in the PDF
press the EDIT button and select your default text editor
(Notepad on windows, vim on linux, SimpleText on mac).

Step 4:

	When finished editing, save the file and return to Step 1.

Step 5:

	Once everything is ready, finish off by pressing the "Convert Selected Files" button
Then select where you would like to save your PDF